title: Best of the Program | Guests: Kelly Shackleford & Sen. Mike Lee | 5/3/22
description:
Pat Gray joins to discuss the Left's meltdown over Roe v. Wade being overturned. President and CEO of First Liberty Institute Kelly Shackleford joins to give some insight on the Supreme Court leak and what this will mean for the country. Sen. Mike Lee discusses the Supreme Court leak and Roe v. Wade.
